videos_data.title: X Dekho | HBL PSL Official Anthem 2025 | #AliZafar #AbrarUlHaq #TalhaAnjum #NatashaBaig #ApnaXHai
videos_data.description:
A decade of passion, a legacy of greatness. Presenting "X Dekho" – the official anthem of HBL PSL 2025, celebrating 10 electrifying years of cricket, fandom, and unforgettable moments.
This anthem isn’t just a song, it’s a call to all cricket lovers to bring their X factor to the biggest season yet. 

#HBLPSL10 #ApnaXHai

Produced by Ali Zafar & Ali Mustafa

comments.text: ​In the Pakistan Super League (PSL) 2025 season, Australian cricketer David Warner emerged as the highest-paid player. This marks a significant increase in the PSL's Platinum category salary cap, which was previously between $130,000 and $170,000. The Pakistan Cricket Board (PCB) raised this cap to a range of $220,000 to $300,000 for the 2025 season to attract top-tier talent.
